summary: I just noticed the line “when you love someone you’ll do crazy things” we see a quick glimpse of Villanelle in the red outfit -...
question: I just noticed the line “when you love someone you’ll do crazy things” we see a quick glimpse of Villanelle in the red outfit - seems like it’s the outfit from the BTS pics of her and Eve in Rome. Do you think, like before season 1 where we had the ‘think about you all the time’ line in the trailers - that this could possibly be from the final ep?
answer:
I didn’t watch or follow anything about Killing Eve when it was aired last year. So, I have no idea what the lines in the trailer are in what episode, sorry.

At first, I thought the line “When you love someone, you will do crazy things” would be said to her hospital mate. But, from the trailer seems like she says to someone that she opens up to enough (I guess Eve). She might say it to her when they work together. I think they might meet around 2x05.

I re-watched the trailer, it clearly shows that Villanelle said this line in her hospital patient gown.

So., she said that line to her patient mate.

summary: fave ladies i believe there is a female assassin operating internationally, and she’s targeted a number of influential people....
caption:
fave ladies

i believe there is a female assassin operating internationally, and she’s targeted a number of influential people. she doesn’t have a signature, but she certainly has style, and i don’t know who or what is behind her, but i don’t think she’s slowing down, and that just interested me…i guess. …but also, apparently makes me a fantasist and a crackpot and completely on my own and you know what? frankly, i don’t give a shit anymore. she is outsmarting the smartest of us and for that, she deserves to do or kill whoever the hell she wants. i mean, if she’s not killing me, then frankly, it’s not my job to care anymore!

summary: Okay I just did a tumblr purge and now my dash is kind of dead and I want new people to follow. Reblog this if you’re into the...
body:
Okay I just did a tumblr purge and now my dash is kind of dead and I want new people to follow. Reblog this if you’re into the stuff below and I’ll check you out!

- critical role

- captain marvel (or any marvel movies, except if you’re a tony stan, we just won’t work if tony is ur favorite avenger)

- lesbians

- pretty things (and not like pretentious pictures of skinny white girls with tattoos and nikes in bathtubs. I’m talking pictures of Iceland and foggy marshes.)

- memes

- a profound lack of bad news. Seriously, if you post a lot of really negative news stories we won’t jive. I’ve been trying to focus on the good in the world lately and I wanna follow people who facilitate that.

- westworld

- Assassins creed odyssey

- the last of us (specifically Ellie)

- uncharted (specifically chlodine)

- writing/screenwriting/film/fan fiction

- killing eve

- Spider-Man into the spiderverse

- other assorted feminist, gay, and/or progressive things

summary: “I was more insecure when I was 20 than I am at 47. At 47 it’s like, “You need me to put on a crazy dress with mirrors? Yeah,...
caption: “I was more insecure when I was 20 than I am at 47. At 47 it’s like, “You need me to put on a crazy dress with mirrors? Yeah, sure. I’m going to work the shit out of this!” I don’t know what I’m doing. It’s, like, you give less fucks. [..] Aging is the greatest. It really gives you more space to be that person in the mirrored dress who has always been inside.”  — Sandra Oh for InStyle.
